(101, 'Passport CRIND Limit Change', '<ol>\r\n<li>Click <strong>Tools<br /><br /></strong></li>\r\n<li>Click <strong>Manager Workstation </strong>(must log in with manager level access)<br /><br /></li>\r\n<li>Click <strong>Setup<br /><br /></strong></li>\r\n<li>Click <strong>Network Menu<br /><br /></strong></li>\r\n<li>Click <strong>Concord<br /><br /></strong></li>\r\n<li>Click <strong>Network <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Card</span> Configuration</strong></li>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>You will be shown the card table. To change card options, click on the card.<br /><br /></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<li>Set the <strong>Crind Auth Amount</strong> and/or <strong>AVS Zip Code Prompt </strong>to set AVS.</li>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Cards requiring AVS must be set to <strong>Outside</strong> in the option.<br /><br /></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<li>Click Save!</li>\r\n</ol>', '2012-08-18 13:13:26', 'l7d23b', '2017-08-03 13:29:05', 'l7d23b', 'yes', 'no', '', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'How to change crind limits on a Gilbarco Passport', '', 10006, 'Tech Support 1', 'N', ''),
