(201, 'Information on 1099k Requests', '<p>If a distributor calls in looking for 1099-K information, please take their information down with a contact number and e-mail and let David Neeley know what they need. &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>We can supply them with the actual 1099 K or a spreadsheet with their data for any distributor for 2011 &ndash; going forward.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Update @ 1/20/17:</strong></p>\r\n<p>There was a list of distributors that requested the form and data by email last year.&nbsp;David Neeley&nbsp;sent a message to each of the email addresses on the list to ask them to confirm their identity and let him know whether the data was needed again.</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"upload/docs/requests for emailed data.xlsx\" target=\"_blank\">Spreadsheet link</a>: the distributors shaded in grey have been sent their forms and data by email. The ones shaded otherwise either had a bad address or didn&rsquo;t need the data. Those that are unshaded have not responded to David.</p>', '2013-08-08 08:48:24', 'l7d23b', '2017-01-20 08:37:14', 'l7d23b', 'yes', 'no', '', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'Information on 1099k Requests', '', 50007, 'Tech Support 1', 'N', '\r\n Supreme Oil Andy Bartotto Dekalb Petroleum Abby Bazille Jobber # Name Contact Southern Petroleum Amy Nickell anickell@spetroleum.net Petromax Oil Inc admin@petromaxoil.com Urvana Gene Harris Pet Inc Lisa Wright lisawright1943@yahoo.com McEvoy Oil Sue Vaughan sue@mcevoyoil.com Knight Enterprises Debbie Gabel debbieg@knightenterprisesinc.com linda.williams@sampsonbladen.com Linda Williams Sampson Bladen Karen Gann kgann@jonespetroleum.com Stark Properties Victory Petroleum ibon@victorypetroleum.com Gordon Environmental groperti@hylangroup.com Dominy Oil Company lindah@jetfoodstores.com WSCO Petroleum Fernando Trujillo Oil Products Distributors int contact Nate Berdon amcnett@gpminvestments.com Mary King Justin Stallings Don Linville Sharon Littlejohn Karey Black Brent Hix opd@oilproducts.biz GPM Petr