(322, 'FIS Merchant Payments Maintenance Schedule 2015', '<p>FIS have again this year reviewed their approach to scheduled maintenance and as such have implemented a rolling weekly program to enable more effective planning and to provide our clients with sufficient notice.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Also indicated are&nbsp;secondary maintenance slots.&nbsp;FIS may not need to utilise all of the windows proposed, but have included them within this schedule in order to provide a further window of contingency.</p>\r\n<p>In the unlikely event there are any issues during a period of maintenance, please contact the FIS Service Desk in the usual manner.</p>\r\n<p>Please note Severity 1 issues should be raised via a phone call in the first instance, with a&nbsp;subsequent following email for an assured speedy response.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"upload/MPS Maintenance Schedule 2015.xlsx\" target=\"_blank\">Access the Maintenance Schedule for 2015 here.</a></p>', '2015-03-13 09:58:46', 'l7d23b', '2015-03-13 10:00:39', 'l7d23b', 'yes', 'no', '', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'FIS Merchant Payments Maintenance Schedule 2015', '', 80002, 'UK Support 1', 'N', '\r\n sat sun mon tue wed thur fri thu January WREn BIRMINGHAM MAINTENANCE CUMBERNAULD MAINTENANCE February March April May June July August September October November December IT Infrastructure IHCF Maintenance Unused Maintenance -BI Maintenance -CU Maintenance Birmingham Cumbernauld Cells 24th Nov 14 to 5th Jan 15 IT Christmas Freeze 2014 IT Christmas Freeze FIS Merchant Payments Maintenance Schedule 2015 IHCF BI IHCF CU CUMBERN\'D MAINTENANCE IT infrastructure<t xml:space=\"preserve\">Maintenance - BI  Secondary Maintenance - Cu'),
(323, 'Sagenet NMS Access', '<p>You can access&nbsp;Sagenet NMS here:</p>\r\n<p>NMS 4.0 -&nbsp;<a href=\"https://148.78.100.12/insite/\">https://148.78.100.12/insite/</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>Fortinet Username</strong>: <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">wts-ama</span><br /><strong>Fortinet Password</strong>: <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">valero</span></p>\r\n<p>NMS Username: <a href=\"mailto:wts-ama@valero.com\">wts-ama@valero.com<br /></a>NMS Password: valeros</p>\r\n<p><br />There may be an invalid security certificate warning you\'ll need to click \"<strong>Continue to this website (not recommended)</strong>\" to continue.</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; display: block;\" src=\"upload/articles/nms/warning.PNG\" alt=\"\" width=\"521\" height=\"224\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>Login Information</h3>\r\n<p><strong>Fortinet Username</strong>: <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">wts-ama</span><br /><br /><strong>Fortinet Password</strong>: <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">valero</span></p>\r\n<p><img style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; display: block;\" src=\"upload/forinet-sn-login.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"499\" height=\"347\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Once logged in you will need to select <strong>MON</strong> - <strong>Monitoring</strong>.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<img style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; display: block;\" src=\"upload/nms-welcome-page.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"634\" height=\"344\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>You will be presented with the following screen after selecting <strong>Monitoring</strong>.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<img style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; display: block;\" src=\"upload/nms-monitoring-screen.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"815\" height=\"342\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>To search for the site in NMS, type in the \"<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">function location</span>\" number into the Search field.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The function location number consists of 3 sets of numbers - (<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">Prysm billing code-Jobber #-Dealer #</span>).&nbsp; For a list of current Prysm billing codes, <a href=\"index.php?pagereq=article&amp;view=article&amp;artid=140\" target=\"_blank\">click here</a>.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; display: block;\" src=\"upload/nms-monitoring-search.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"825\" height=\"271\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Click the magnifying glass to see the even history of the site.</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; display: block;\" src=\"upload/nms-monitoring-history.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"835\" height=\"341\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">Status History</span> screen will give you the latest events from the site. If you need to go back futher than what is displayed, click the<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"> Export</span> button with Excel selected. This will open a spread sheet of events. <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>Warning</strong></span>: the Excel file can be quite large and may take a moment to download.</p>\r\n<p>You are also able to ping the prysm from this screen. This is useful for site diagnostics.</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>Note:</strong></span> Spacenet can&nbsp;also search sites by the workorder number as well as the&nbsp;Functional Location.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '2015-03-25 08:21:21', 'l7d23b', '2017-06-20 12:16:45', 'ln524h', 'yes', 'no', '', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'Information on Sagenet Network Monitoring System', '', 40005, 'Tech Support 1', 'N', 'https://148.78.100.12/insite/mailto:wts-ama@valero.comindex.php?pagereq=article&amp;view=article&amp;artid=140'),
(324, 'AT&T U-Verse Modem Issues', '<p>There is an auto update feature on the U-Verse modems that can cause intermittent processing issues or cause processing to fail around the same time every day on our IP based sites. This setting can be disabled.</p>\r\n<p>When having AT&amp;T disable this setting, also have them extend the lease time to 7 days or more to further improve stability.</p>', '2015-03-27 12:43:38', 'l7d23b', '2015-03-27 12:44:22', 'l7d23b', 'yes', 'no', '', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'ATT Uverse Modem Issues', '', 30006, 'Tech Support 1', 'N', '');
