(397, 'Imprinter Ordering', '<h3>New Station&nbsp;Setup</h3>\r\n<p><a href=\"mailto:customerservice@gcfinc.com?CC=mitzi.land@valero.com; israel.herrera@valero.com; karey.black@valero.com; debbie.green@valero.com&amp;Subject=OPENMEFIRST&amp;Body=Please%20process%20this%20order%20for%20the%20site%20listed%20below%20and%20ship%20directly%20to%20the%20site.%20%0A%20%20%0AJobber-Dealer%20%0ASite%20Name%20%0ASite%20Address%20%0ACity/State/Zip%20%0ASite%20Phone%20%0A%0AThe%20part%20number%20will%20be%20OPENMEFIRST.%20%20The%20contents%20of%20this%20kit%20will%20be%20the%20following%3A%0A2%20pkgs%20of%20VLO1085%27s%20-%20Manual%20Invoice%20%0A2%20pkgs%20of%201029%27s%20-%20Transmittal%20Summary%20%0A2%20pkgs%20of%201063%27s%20-%20Credit%20Card%20Transmittal%20%0A2%20pkgs%20of%2069FC%27s%20-%20Mailing%20Envelopes%20%0A1%20ea%20of%20D4850%20Manual%20Imprinter%20%0A1%20ea%20of%20SP211%20Metal%20Plate%20%0A%0AThank%20you.%20\">Click here to send an email order for an imprinter kit for a <strong>new station</strong></a>.</p>\r\n<p>This will include the following</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>2 pkgs. of VLO1085\'s - Manual Invoice</li>\r\n<li>2 pkgs of 1029\'s - Transmittal Summary</li>\r\n<li>2 pkgs of 1063\'s - Credit Card Transmittal</li>\r\n<li>2 pkgs of 69FC\'s - Mailing Envelopes</li>\r\n<li>1&nbsp;ea of D4850 -&nbsp;Manual Imprinter</li>\r\n<li>1 ea of SP211 -&nbsp;Metal Plate</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>Plate Only Request</h3>\r\n<p><a href=\"mailto:customerservice@gcfinc.com?CC=mitzi.land@valero.com; israel.herrera@valero.com; karey.black@valero.com; debbie.green@valero.com&amp;Subject=Plate%20Request&amp;Body=Please%20process%20this%20order%20for%20the%20site%20listed%20below%20and%20ship%20directly%20to%20the%20site.%20%20%0A%20%20%0AJobber-Dealer%20%0ASite%20Name%20%0ASite%20Address%20%0ACity/State/Zip%20%0ASite%20Phone%20%0A%0ASite%20is%20requiring%20an%20imprinter%20plate%20with%20the%20information%20listed%20above.%20%0A%0A1%20count%20of%3A%20SP211%20Metal%20Plate%2