(401, 'Dealer Transfer', '<h3>Transferring a Dealer</h3>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>You will receive notification through the branded analyst.</li>\r\n<li>You need to create a file jobber.dealer.txt to move the current dealer to the new jobber number and save on the n:\\ drive to be processed by Jerry Cook and Donna Brasher. <br />*Please follow the<a href=\"O:\\AMA-CC\\Branding Request/templatejobber.dealernotes.txt\" target=\"_blank\"> format templatejobber.dealernotes.txt </a>for details on formatting.</li>\r\n<li>Be sure to deactivate any current billing codes on the old jobber/dealer records.</li>\r\n<li>Make a note in RAMS on the merchant notes screen of the transfer going from and to as follows:&nbsp;<br />\r\n<table style=\"height: 23px; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;\" width=\"518\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>&nbsp;TRSF</p>\r\n<p>Transferred from 45500-12345&nbsp;</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>TRSF</p>\r\n<p>Transferred to 65500-12345</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>The dealer will need a new plate, sales guide and 2 orange plastics.</li>\r\n<li>Update the profile at FD of the new jobber #.</li>\r\n<li><a href=\"mailto:susan.torres@firstdata.com; Barbara.Hockenberry@firstdata.com ?CC=mitzi.land@valero.com; karey.black@valero.com; israel.herrera@valero.com; debbie.green@valero.com&amp;Subject=IRS%20Name%20and%20Tax%20ID&amp;Body=Please%20change%20the%20IRS%20Name%20and%20Tax%20ID%20for%20the%20site%20that%20has%20transferred%20to%20another%20distributor.%0A%0AIRS%20Name%3A%20%0ATax%20ID%3A%0A%0A6-Digit%20BP%0AJobber-Dealer%0AStation%20Name%0AStation%20Address%0ACity%2C%20State%20Zip%0A%0AThank%20you%21\">Click here to Email&nbsp;First Data with the new IRS Name and Tax ID</a>.&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li><a href=\"mailto: ?CC=mitzi.land@valero.com; karey.black@valero.com; israel.herrera@valero.com; debbie.green@valero.com&amp;Subject=Dealer%20Transfer%20Completed&amp;Body=This%20site%20has%20been%20completed.%20The%20merchant%20id%20%23%20will%20not%20change.%20I%20will%20send%20the%20site%20a%20new%20plate%20and%20supplies.%20I%20have%20made%20the%20necessary%20changes%20for%20the%20new%20distributor%20to%20receive%20the%20money.%0A%0A6-Digit%20BP%0AJobber-Dealer%0AStation%20Name%0AStation%20Address%0ACity%2C%20State%20Zip%0A%0AThank%20you%21\">Click here to send an email to branded analyst that you have completed the transfer</a>.</li>\r\n</ol>', '2015-12-03 13:22:31', 'l7d23b', '2017-03-15 13:30:10', 'l7d23b', 'yes', 'no', '', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'Dealer Transfer', '', 40014, 'Tech Support 2', 'N', 'mailto:susan.torres@firstdata.com; Barbara.Hockenberry@firstdata.com ?CC=mitzi.land@valero.com; karey.black@valero.com; israel.herrera@valero.com; debbie.green@valero.com&amp;Subject=IRS Name and Tax ID&amp;Body=Please change the IRS Name and Tax ID for the site that has transferred to another distributor.%0A%0AIRS Name%3A %0ATax ID%3A%0A%0A6-Digit BP%0AJobber-Dealer%0AStation Name%0AStation Address%0ACity%2C State Zip%0A%0AThank you%21mailto: ?CC=mitzi.land@valero.com; karey.black@valero.com; israel.herrera@valero.com; debbie.green@valero.com&amp;Subject=Dealer Transfer Completed&amp;Body=This site has been completed. The merchant id %23 will not change. I will send the site a new plate and supplies. I have made the necessary changes for the new distributor to receive the money.%0A%0A6-Digit BP%0AJobber-Dealer%0AStation Name%0AStation Address%0ACity%2C State Zip%0A%0AThank you%21'),
(402, 'Unbranded Site Setup', '<h3>Set up an unbranded site</h3>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>In RAMS, you will need to make the following changes:\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type: lower-alpha;\">\r\n<li>STA TYPE field needs to be a U</li>\r\n<li>DISC GRP field needs to be NSTNF or NSONF (depending on state)</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>In Online Boarding, you will need to make the following changes:</li>\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type: lower-alpha;\">\r\n<li>Select unbranded for the merchant type</li>\r\n<li>Uncheck the flags for Valero Fleet &amp; Diamond Shamrock proprietary cards</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h3>When site goes branded</h3>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>In RAMS, you will need to make the following changes:\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type: lower-alpha;\">\r\n<li>STA TYPE field needs to be a S.</li>\r\n<li>DISC GRP field needs to be STOFL or TSOFL (depending on state &amp; type of connection)</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Send an email to Aisha at First Data to make the following changes:\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type: lower-alpha;\">\r\n<li>Turn on Valero Fleet &amp; Diamond Shamrock proprietary cards</li>\r\n<li>Change BANK-MERCH FIIDS to CNPF-QY66 or CNPH-QY67 depending on whether the site has an integrated or non-integrated system</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>', '2015-12-03 13:29:22', 'l7d23b', '2015-12-03 13:29:22', 'l7d23b', 'yes', 'no', '', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'Unbranded Site Setup', '', 40014, 'Tech Support 2', 'N', ''),
(403, 'Debrand on VX570', '<ol>\r\n<li>On the date of <strong>DEBRAND</strong>, you will change the status on RAMS to show deactivated.</li>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>On the command line type in <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">MDEL</span></li>\r\n<li>Tab over to the code line type in <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">D</span>.</li>\r\n<li>Press the enter key.&nbsp;<br /><br /></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<li>If there is a Vx570 and/or Satellite billing, make the deactivation date the last date of the billing cycle.</li>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>On the command line type in <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">DVDD</span>.</li>\r\n<li>On the date line use the debrand date.</li>\r\n<li>Press the enter key.<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<li><a href=\"mailto:deric.thames@firstdata.com?CC=deric.thames@firstdata.com; mitzi.land@valero.com; karey.black@valero.com; israel.herrera@valero.com; debbie.green@valero.com&amp;Subject=Valero%20Inactive%20Site&amp;Body=Please%20change%20the%20following%20site%20profile%20to%20inactive%3A%0A%0A6-Digit%20BP%20MID%0AJobber-Dealer%0ASite%20Name%0ASite%20Address%0ACity%2C%20State%20Zip%0A%0AThank%20you%21\">Click here to email&nbsp;Deric at First Data</a>.</li>\r\n</ol>', '2015-12-03 13:32:49', 'l7d23b', '2016-11-29 05:00:44', 'l7d23b', 'yes', 'no', '', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'Debrand on VX570', '', 40014, 'Tech Support 2', 'N', 'mailto:deric.thames@firstdata.com?CC=deric.thames@firstdata.com; mitzi.land@valero.com; karey.black@valero.com; israel.herrera@valero.com; debbie.green@valero.com&amp;Subject=Valero Inactive Site&amp;Body=Please change the following site profile to inactive%3A%0A%0A6-Digit BP MID%0AJobber-Dealer%0ASite Name%0ASite Address%0ACity%2C State Zip%0A%0AThank you%21'),
