(405, 'Use Tax Explanation', '<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Use tax is the charge that is passed to stores on any electronic POS or manual transactions that we process here in Amarillo for sales that originated in Texas. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">The amount is calculated on the total transaction fees for the month multiplied by the tax rate for Amarillo TX (Total Monthly Transaction Fees X 0.0825= Use Tax).&nbsp;</span> </span></p>', '2015-12-15 14:36:38', 'lbfb2t', '2017-06-18 11:41:52', 'ln524h', 'yes', 'no', '', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'Explanation on Use Tax and how it is calculated', '', 50007, 'Tech Support 1', 'N', ''),
(406, 'First Data Online Boarding', '<p>Once logged in to OLB the following screen will be displayed.</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"upload/olb1x.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"811\" height=\"652\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Merchant Type\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Company Owned</li>\r\n<li>Jobber</li>\r\n<li>Unbranded</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Jobber Dealer Number</li>\r\n<li>DBA Name</li>\r\n<li>Store Number</li>\r\n<li>IRS Business Name</li>\r\n<li>Federal Tax ID</li>\r\n<li>Contact</li>\r\n<li>Address 1</li>\r\n<li>Address 2</li>\r\n<li>City</li>\r\n<li>State</li>\r\n<li>Zip</li>\r\n<li>Email</li>\r\n<li>Phone</li>\r\n<li>Fax</li>\r\n<li>Cut Time</li>\r\n<li>Time Zone</li>\r\n<li>Daylight Savings &amp; Var Cut</li>\r\n<li>Prop ID</li>\r\n<li>Terminal Type\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>L3 Gilbarco Passport</li>\r\n<li>TP Verifone Ruby/Sapphire/Commander</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Encryption\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>None</li>\r\n<li>DUKPT</li>\r\n<li>Triple DES DUKPT</li>\r\n<li>Buypass</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</li>\r\n<li># Terminals</li>\r\n<li>Velocity</li>\r\n<li>Velocity $ Amount</li>\r\n<li>Fuelman ID</li>\r\n<li>Fleet One ID</li>\r\n<li>Card Acceptant Checkboxes</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '2015-12-18 09:46:44', 'l7d23b', '2015-12-18 09:53:00', 'l7d23b', 'no', 'no', '', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'Information on using Online Boarding', '', 40014, 'Tech Support 2', 'N', ''),
(407, 'Mastercard Fleet Velocity Setup', '<ol>\r\n<li><strong>Uncheck the MC Fleet Velocity button. This also unchecks the Velocity button. <br /><img style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; display: block;\" src=\"upload/mcvelo1.PNG\" alt=\"\" width=\"659\" height=\"366\" /><br /><br /></strong></li>\r\n<li><strong>Recheck the Velocity button and Update.<br /><img style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; display: block;\" src=\"upload/mcvelo2.PNG\" alt=\"\" width=\"663\" height=\"371\" /><br /><br /><br /></strong></li>\r\n<li><strong>Select the Submit button to refresh the screen<br /><img style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; display: block;\" src=\"upload/mcvelo3.PNG\" alt=\"\" width=\"671\" height=\"374\" /><br /></strong></li>\r\n</ol>', '2015-12-18 12:23:04', 'l7d23b', '2015-12-18 12:23:04', 'l7d23b', 'yes', 'no', '', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'Mastercard Fleet Velocity Setup', '', 40002, 'Tech Support 1', 'N', ''),
(408, 'Acumera Pilot Sites', '<p>We will be migrating 13 &amp; Hoover Valero from TNS FPX to Acumera Processor Connections on March 24th for credit card processing.&nbsp; If the site calls in to report issues with the AMG, please open a ticket, then transfer the customer to Acumera at 512-687-7401.&nbsp; This is Valero&rsquo;s fourth site to test the Processor Connections offer from Acumera.&nbsp; The migration will consist of:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Acumera installing the AMG with the Processor Connections applications and an 8-port managed switch</li>\r\n<li>POS tech de-installing the Verifone Sapphire and installing a Verifone Commander</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>o&nbsp;&nbsp; updating the POS with an IP &amp; host information for First Data</p>\r\n<p>o&nbsp;&nbsp; Connecting the isolated payment NIC to the managed switch</p>\r\n<p>o&nbsp;&nbsp; Connect the EZR to the managed switch</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The site will be using broadband primary with 4G for failover.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Site Details:</p>\r\n<p>Jobber&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 3450</p>\r\n<p>Dealer&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 29256</p>\r\n<p>Site Name&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 13 &amp; Hoover Valero</p>\r\n<p>Address&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 11550 13 MILE RD, Warren, MI 48093</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Here are the details for the POS:</p>\r\n<p>IP POS&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 172.16.21.12</p>\r\n<p>GW&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nb