(444, 'Heat Changes', '<p>Beginning tomorrow August 26th. Heat will not longer, by default, open to a blank UK ticket upon opening a new ticket. When a new ticket is launched, it will show the \"Customer Type\" selection (same as ctrl+t).</p>\r\n<p>This change will not affect our UK group. They will still have the UK ticket open by default.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; display: block;\" src=\"upload/customer type.PNG\" alt=\"\" width=\"581\" height=\"200\" /></p>', '2016-08-25 10:42:39', 'l7d23b', '2016-08-25 10:42:39', 'l7d23b', 'no', 'no', '', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'Changes to Heat', '', 60002, 'Tech Support 1', 'N', '');
