(480, 'Empire Acquisition of CST Sites', '<p><a href=\"upload/docs/Empire Site Roll Out Final Schedule.xlsx\" target=\"_blank\">Conversion Schedule XLS</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"acuvigil.acumera.net\" target=\"_blank\">Acuvigil</a></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">UPDATE 9/07/17:</span></strong>&nbsp; There is a known issue at the moment with these sites having a stable connection to the network.&nbsp; Credit processing is intermittent.&nbsp; Acumera is working on a fix at the moment.&nbsp; If you have a problem with a site, please check with Acumera.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Empire has acquired a large group of sites from CST and will begin converting them on September 6<sup>th</sup>, the schedule is above.&nbsp; All sites will be installed with an Acumera AMG for payment processing.&nbsp; When the tech calls in, please perform the following steps.&nbsp; All Acumera AMG&rsquo;s were pre-activated, so when the tech connects it to an Internet connection, the AMG should come online.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Confirm the Acumera Managed Gateway is online in AcuVigil\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>If the AMG does not come online, confirm connections<br /><br /></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>The sapphire First Network must be configured for Enhanced_Hughes_VSAT\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Data Bits: 8</li>\r\n<li>Parity: None</li>\r\n<li>Stop Bits: 1</li>\r\n<li><strong>Dial phone number is 77090001</strong><br /><br /></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Confirm the tech has the proprietary blue cable from Acumera &ndash; One end of the cable is an RJ45, the other end is an RJ12\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>The RJ45 end of the cable will directly connect to Com 2 of the Sapphire, the RJ12 end of the cable will directly connect to the AMG in the RS232 Port 1.&nbsp; There should be no connector inline between the Sapphire and the AMG.<br /><br /></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Confirm the merchant ID</li>\r\n<li><strong>Buynet&nbsp;will need to be set to 931699</strong></li>\r\n<li>Set the site for a PDL</li>\r\n<li>Ask tech to test credit</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Once the items have been confirmed and the site is processing credit, please close the activation ticket in AcuVigil.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Select site</li>\r\n<li>On banner, under store number, select Support\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>This will open support tickets<br /><br /></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Select open install ticket</li>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Scroll to bottom, update ticket with notes on successful install, select reply</li>\r\n<li><strong>Scroll to top of ticket, hover over Waiting on Customer, select Closed</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</ul>', '2017-09-01 10:57:41', 'l7d23b', '2017-09-07 16:08:46', 'lbfb2t', 'yes', 'no', '', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'Empire Acquisition of CST Sites', '', 10003, 'Tech Support 1', 'N', '\r\n Date DOW Region 1 (ROG 1) (EPP 1) Region 2  (ROG 1) (EPP 2) Region 3 (ROG 1) (EPP 3) Region 4 (ROG 1)  (EPP 3) Region 5  (ROG 1) (EPP 2) CORPUS CHRISTI/AUSTIN/SHREVEPORT ALBUQUERQUE/COLORADO TUCSON/COLORADO PHOENIX/COLORADO EL PASO Wed Thur Fri Sun Travel to Austin  (ROG 1) (EPP 1) Travel to Colorado (ROG 1) (EPP 2) Travel to Colorado (ROG 1) (EPP 2)\r\nFloater (EPP 1) No changes (ROG 1) (EPP 3) No changes (ROG 1) (EPP 2) Mon Tues Travel to Shreveport (ROG 1) (EPP 1)<t xml:space=\"preserve\">428 (641785)/8187-Corpus Christi\r\n1503 (645753)/8188-Corpus Christi\r\n\r\n\r\n 1242 (645269)/8162-Albuquerque\r\n1240 (645136)/8161-Albuquerque 1627 (645956)/8145-Tucson\r\n1613 (646001)/8143-Tucson 1654 (645982)/8139-Gilbert\r\n1701 (666331)/8125- Gilbert 1746 (667627)/8175-El Paso\r\n1277 (645306)/8168-El Paso 1828 (341761)/8189-Corpus Christi\r\n43 (640830)/8192-North Corpus Cristi 1219 (645114)/8160-Albuquerque\r\n1216 (645121)/8159-Albuquerque 1658 (645983)/8148-Tucson\r\n1617 (645871)/8144-Tucson\r\n1636 (645969)/8146-Tucson 1611 (645869)/8136-Phoenix\r\n1651 (645978)/8138-Phoenix\r\n1618 (646027)/8137-Phoenix<t xml:space=\"preserve\">1357 (645460)/8171-El Paso\r\n1369 