(344, 'l7d23b', 'no', 'Texaco Staton Settlement Reports', '<p><span style=\"text-decoration: line-through;\">There are currently no settlement reports on the Texaco Station website. Due to incorrect data in the reports, they&nbsp;have been pulled and are are being re-run. We currently do not have an ETA for the new reports.</span></p>\r\n<p>The reports are now available.</p>', 'UK Support 1', '2017-06-19 09:25:02'),
(345, 'lbfb2t', 'no', 'Verifone EMV/Rapid Connect Info', '<p>We have some pilot sites setting up VeriFone EMV/Rapid Connect.&nbsp; Please go <a href=\"O:\\AMA-CC\\WTS-Wholesale Technical Support\\Reflex Articles\\Valero-NetCfg.06222017.pdf\">here</a>&nbsp;to look at configuration guide. If you have any questions, please contact Kimberly Ford.&nbsp;</p>', 'Tech Support 1', '2017-06-23 17:16:39'),
(346, 'ln524h', 'yes', 'ASM Billing Credits', '<p>Some locations were recently double billed for ASM (VeriFone Maintenance&nbsp;program).&nbsp; These locations should see credits on their MSR to correct the double billing.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>These&nbsp;sites&nbsp;upgraded their POS equipment and opted to purchase 1 year of ASM with VeriFone (or another 3<sup>rd</sup> party vendor) and pay up front for it. &nbsp;However, Valero was unaware of this, so we continued to bill them every month.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Denise Arispe sent each distributor an email with the affected sites.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"upload/docs/copy-of-contract-admin-list.xlsx\" target=\"_blank\">Click here</a> for a&nbsp;list of sites that have received credit on this issue.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'Tech Support 1', '2017-07-05 12:00:18'),
(347, 'l7d23b', 'yes', 'Gempay 3 Heat Ticket Coding', '<p><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>Urgent</strong></span>: Beginning immediately, please log all Gempay 3 calls at our pilot sites under the HEAT Record Type, &ldquo;<strong>13 ROI &ndash; Problem&rdquo;</strong>.</p>', 'UK Support 1', '2017-07-07 06:40:08'),
(349, 'l7d23b', 'yes', 'Allocations and Pricing', '<p>Allocation - Site needs to contact their Territory Manager.</p>\r\n<p>Pricing -&nbsp;Site can call their contract admin to research as the why they are not receiving but should be going thru DTN.</p>', 'Tech Support 1', '2017-07-12 08:45:50'),
(351, 'l7d23b', 'yes', 'MFL Cash Back Removal', '<p>MFL (MFG) locations have had cashback removed by request from their head office. &nbsp;If they have questions, they will need to contact MFL (MFG)&rsquo;s head office.</p>', 'UK Support 1', '2017-07-14 10:03:36'),
(354, 'lqnwmy', 'no', 'Direct Links to Customer Portal and Fleet Portal', '<p>Currently, we are experiencing issues with access to the Wholesale Portal. Below are direct links to the Fleet Portal and the Consumer Card Portal:</p>\r\n<p>Fleet:&nbsp; <a href=\"https://ccc.valero.com/fams/\">https://ccc.valero.com/fams/</a></p>\r\n<p>Consumer:&nbsp;&nbsp; <a href=\"https://ccc.valero.com/mycard/SignIn.aspx\">https://ccc.valero.com/mycard/SignIn.aspx</a></p>\r\n<p>These links can be provided to the customers for quick access if necessary.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'Tech Support 1', '2017-07-17 08:11:33'),
(355, 'l7d23b', 'yes', 'Gempay3 Pilot Extension', '<p>Starting Monday, we will be extending the Gempay 3 to a further 10 sites, bringing the total number of deployed sites to 22.</p>\r\n<table style=\"width: 465px; height: 124px;\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 166px; font-weight: 400; border-bottom-color: black; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid;\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt;\">SCHOOL SERVICE STATION (GEMPAY)</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 62px; font-weight: 400; border-bottom-color: black; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid;\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt;\">BD18 1BX</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 30px; font-weight: 400; border-bottom-color: black; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid;\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt;\">VL887138</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 166px; font-weight: 400; border-bottom-color: black; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid;\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt;\">BOXER SERVICE STATION (SPAR PONTHIR)</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 62px; font-weight: 400; border-bottom-color: black; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid;\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt;\">NP18 3NY</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 30px; font-weight: 400; border-bottom-color: black; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid;\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt;\">VL887125</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 166px; font-weight: 400; border-bottom-color: black; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid;\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt;\">BETTWS SERVICE STATION (GEMPAY)</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 62px; font-weight: 400; border-bottom-color: black; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid;\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt;\">NP20 7DB</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 30px; font-weight: 400; border-bottom-color: black; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid;\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt;\">VL886877</s